  <span id="freeText6422063663289950896" style="display:none">Being unmarried and unengaged, this may seem like a strange choice of book. But, loving another human being and desiring to know how to love them better in the end, and in all of that desiring to understand how this brings me closer to Christ, perhaps it's not so strange a choice after all. Few books have reminded me just how deep the love of Christ truly is. Few books have reminded me so poetically (besides, perhaps, A Severe Mercy) how the deepest love in this life is but a glorious shadow of an even more glorious Love. So go find a copy of this book, whether in love, married, or neither. </span>
